<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>수정하기</title>
  <style>
    body {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .edit-form {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      padding: 40px;
      width: 400px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    input[type="text"],
    textarea {
      width: 300px;
      height: 30px;
      padding: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    textarea {
      height: 200px;
    }

    p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    input[type="submit"] {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
      height: 30px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      width: 100px;
    }

    input[type="submit"]:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }

    a {
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="edit-form">
      <h1>수정하기</h1>
      <form action="/board/edit/<%= post.id %>" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목" value="<%= post.title %>">
        <textarea name="content" placeholder="내용"><%= post.content %></textarea>
        <p>게시물을 진짜로 수정하십니까? 수정을 거부할 권리가 있다는 사실 및 수정 거부에 따른 불이익이 있는 경우에는 그 불이익의 내용은 비밀입니다.</p>
        <input type="submit" value="수정하기">
      </form>
      <p><a href="/board">게시판으로 돌아가기</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
